      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so much weight to carry. if the real me is already dead, then what's the point of this empty shell just continuing to exist? it feels like i'm just haunting my own life. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just let the rest of it go? to finally stop the charade?",
